%N A086611 Row sums of triangle of coefficients (A086610) where T(n,k) is the coefficient of x^n*y^k in f(x,y) that satisfies f(x,y) = (1-x-x^2)/(1-x)^2 + xy*f(x,y)^2.
%F A086611 G.f.: A(x) = (1-x-x^2)/(1-x)^2 + x*A(x)^2.
%F A086611 From _Seiichi Manyama_, Mar 03 2026: (Start)
%F A086611 a(0) = 1; a(n) = 2 - n + Sum_{k=0..n-1} a(k) * a(n-1-k).
%F A086611 G.f.: (1 - sqrt(1 - 4*x*(1 + 2*x/(1-x) - x/(1-x)^2)))/(2*x). (End)
%e A086611 a(3) = -1+1+6+5 = 11, a(4) = -2-2+6+20+14 = 36, a(5) = -3-6-4+30+70+42 = 129.
%Y A086611 Cf. A086610 (triangle), A086616, A086632, A110886.
%K A086611 nonn,easy,changed
%O A086611 0,2
